    "description": "Trapped in a secluded mansion, a tiny sparrow must survive deadly encounters with horrific creatures as it unravels the mansion's dark secrets and desperately tries to escape. Explore vents, crawlspaces, secret rooms, and more to uncover the gripping story and world of SPARROW. <strong>DEMO includes first TWO CHAPTERS from the full game.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survival Horror</h2>Experience horror like never before as you play as a tiny bird in a very large world. From the sparrow's perspective, you must navigate through an old mansion with nothing but your wings to guide you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Freedom of Flight</h2>To survive the world of SPARROW, your wings are your main asset. Experience the freedom of movement with the ability to fly throughout your environment. Use your wings to solve puzzles and escape terrifying creatures that normal grounded movement wouldn't allow. Mastering flight is the only way to progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210580/extras/06160a92f4762e498e09c6e6d2fda2b4.poster.avif?t=1728918318\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210580/extras/06160a92f4762e498e09c6e6d2fda2b4.webm?t=1728918318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210580/extras/06160a92f4762e498e09c6e6d2fda2b4.mp4?t=1728918318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210580/extras/9e681124b54330d482e5ec55f911cf2e.poster.avif?t=1728918318\" width=616 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210580/extras/9e681124b54330d482e5ec55f911cf2e.webm?t=1728918318\